name: FixedOrderComparator_addAsEqualTest
description: Unit tests for the addAsEqual method of FixedOrderComparator.

test_cases.name: testAddAsEqual_Success
test_cases.description: Tests the successful addition of an object as equal to an existing object in the FixedOrderComparator.

test_cases.name: testAddAsEqual_ExistingObjNotKnown
test_cases.description: Tests that an IllegalArgumentException is thrown when trying to add an object as equal to a non-existing object in the FixedOrderComparator.

test_cases.name: testAddAsEqual_AlreadyKnown
test_cases.description: Tests that adding an object as equal to an existing object in the FixedOrderComparator returns false if the object is already known.

test_cases.name: testAddAsEqual_LockedComparator
test_cases.description: Tests that an UnsupportedOperationException is thrown when trying to add an object as equal to an existing object in a locked FixedOrderComparator.
